Player: Dungeon Master Note: Current date and time: 1492 Springmonth 1 13:01:00. Player: i need to leave

Dungeon Master: {
  "narration": "As the weight of the day settles over the command post--the rangers bustling with purpose, Commander Elen glancing up from her maps with understanding--you feel exhaustion tug at your bones. Kira notices your weariness and gives a gentle nod. 'You've more than earned a real rest, Eirik. We'll keep watch here, and nothing will slip past us.'\n\nThe silver bell gleams in the afternoon sun, its promise of hope echoing quietly over the outpost as you prepare to take your leave. The warmth of camaraderie, the distant clang of the smithy, and the cautious optimism in the air follow you out, a reminder that though the frontier is not yet safe, its defenders stand ready--and will await your return.",
